item.title: CVE-2017-1356|2024-09-16T16:33:08.278Z -- ibm -- atlas%20ediscovery%20process%20management
item.description: IBM Atlas eDiscovery Process Management 6.0.3 is vulnerable to SQL injection. A remote attacker could send specially-crafted SQL statements, which could allow the attacker to view, add, modify or delete information in the back-end database. IBM X-Force ID: 126683.
